{"tid":1971842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"夾公仔大騙局?","createTime":"2020-04-14T07:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T09:49:39.000Z","uid":355936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31f198feef8d8cce374e71ed92cbdfa955bef25d","tid":1971842,"uid":355936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JcfsLdw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcfsLdw.jpg&h=f63a7d37&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zu8h7rS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzu8h7rS.jpg&h=bddca321&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14jQH0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14jQH0c.jpg&h=22ca30f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88jEBuM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88jEBuM.jpg&h=67d267e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我唔敢講所有夾公仔鋪都係呃人，但咁樣嘅經營手法我唔認同，亦都好唔要得。我明白做生意個個都想賺錢，但都要賺得有良心。<br />\n你話個租80萬，連埋其他野120萬好大開支，雖然我睇到73萬租係指成個場，唔係夾公仔場80萬。咁呢樣野我唔深究。你話你一直都想搵長期客戶，但喺呢個疫情入面你加人地2千蚊租，當然，你話你唔租，出面大把人租，我明，我可以選擇唔續約。<br />\n最嬲嘅係，你開頭話將個約照推遲14日，我覺得合理嘅，但轉個頭你突然要人地4月6日前交租(4月份)，如果唔係就冇得退還部分嘅租金，唔續約嘅就要白白冇左5日租金。原因都係果啲，業主唔肯減租，唔係唔想做好人之類。跟住就係你一大埋所謂嘅「真心說話」。<br />\n你有冇賺到錢你自己最清楚，死無對證。但你咁嘅經營手法，唔好諗住真係搵到長期客戶。"},{"pid":"875fb78719e45a3ad836bf9ef6bafd757af03766","tid":1971842,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d4965497590d5cfba83c2340f4259555de65de8","tid":1971842,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"仲有無野爆?"},{"pid":"a0bed01e65589a98afb121116a2cdf935b76f555","tid":1971842,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"終於有啲圖睇下 支持繼續有野爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93678d43e660747e963952cef82a65fc88935b3","tid":1971842,"uid":354993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"睇完手足判刑覺得嬲嘅入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1971909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1971909</a>"},{"pid":"4ea2f3c406a55d9dc200e5152f3f262a43023658","tid":1971842,"uid":73275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"爆鳩佢地班仆街就岩啦 <br />\n貓哭老鼠假慈悲 成班偽君子"},{"pid":"d3e5467db89036d1be977dc58e2c040e8abfd6a5","tid":1971842,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"香港地跟合約精神<br />\n覺得無錢賺既 5日租都唔蝕得情願繼續交租？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c2bd5c7b34f574ea1bd4253a02688626715606","tid":1971842,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:35:37.000Z","msg":"果班人點敢入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806dbf1be981d02ecc5d7a97fe86b07ceddc4d80","tid":1971842,"uid":355936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e5467db89036d1be977dc58e2c040e8abfd6a5","tid":1971842,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"香港地跟合約精神<br />\n覺得無錢賺既 5日租都唔蝕得情願繼續交租？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔交租分分鐘連按金都拎唔返"},{"pid":"a9fddbf5bb499ed5771ddd8ff9f11c1b959ed9a4","tid":1971842,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"806dbf1be981d02ecc5d7a97fe86b07ceddc4d80","tid":1971842,"uid":355936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e5467db89036d1be977dc58e2c040e8abfd6a5","tid":1971842,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"香港地跟合約精神<br />\n覺得無錢賺既 5日租都唔蝕得情願繼續交租？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔交租分分鐘連按金都拎唔返"},"citedBy":0,"re